<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/godfather.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/stuff/icon/library_books_24dp_14FFEC_FILL0_wght400_GRAD0_opsz24.svg">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        /* Define new color variables */
        :root {
            --vibrant-teal: #1A9D9E;
            --glowing-cyan: #00E7FF;
            --neutral-gray: #4A4A4A;
            --accent-gold: #FFD700;
            --soft-white: #E0E0E0;
        }

        /* Enable vertical scrolling on the page */
        body {
            overflow-y: auto;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black), #1a1a1a);
            color: var(--neutral-gray);
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Main container */
        .about-container {
            max-width: 90%;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            color: var(--neutral-gray);
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Header section */
        .about-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Monoton', serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: var(--vibrant-teal);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.7), 0 0 5px var(--glowing-cyan);
        }

        .about-header h1:hover {
            color: var(--glowing-cyan);
            text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.9), 0 0 10px var(--glowing-cyan);
        }

        .about-header p {
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--neutral-gray);
            opacity: 0.9;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Content sections */
        .about-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, max-height 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Specific styling for expandable sections (Our Story, Our Mission) */
        .expandable {
            max-height: 200px;
        }

        .expandable.expanded {
            max-height: 600px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.3);
        }

        /* Remove max-height constraint for non-expandable sections (Our Values) */
        .non-expandable {
            max-height: none;
            overflow: visible;
        }

        .about-content:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--vibrant-teal);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--vibrant-teal), var(--glowing-cyan));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .about-content:hover h2 {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.8);
        }

        /* Scrolling text container (visible on hover) */
        .scrolling-text {
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
            display: none;
        }

        .expandable:hover .scrolling-text {
            display: block;
        }

        .expandable:hover .static-text {
            display: none;
        }

        .scrolling-text span {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: scroll-text 20s linear infinite;
            color: var(--glowing-cyan);
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0.9;
            padding-left: 100%;
        }

        @keyframes scroll-text {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }
        }

        /* Static text (visible when not hovering) */
        .static-text {
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--soft-white);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        /* Expanded content (visible when clicked) */
        .expanded-content {
            display: none;
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 2;
            color: var(--soft-white);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(10px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .expandable.expanded .expanded-content {
            display: block;
        }

        .expandable.expanded .static-text,
        .expandable.expanded .scrolling-text {
            display: none;
        }

        /* Values section */
        .values-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .value-card {
            background: rgba(26, 157, 158, 0.15);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.25);
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .value-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--vibrant-teal);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 231, 255, 0.5);
            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover h3 {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .value-card p {
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--soft-white);
            line-height: 1.5;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            .about-header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .about-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .static-text, .scrolling-text span, .expanded-content {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .expandable {
                max-height: 160px;
            }

            .expandable.expanded {
                max-height: 500px;
            }

            .about-content {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .value-card h3 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .value-card p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .about-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .about-header p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .about-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .static-text, .scrolling-text span, .expanded-content {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .expandable {
                max-height: 120px;
            }

            .expandable.expanded {
                max-height: 400px;
            }

            .about-content {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .value-card h3 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .value-card p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
    <script nonce="<%= nonce %>">
        // Ensure the script runs after the DOM is loaded
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            console.log('DOM fully loaded, initializing click events for About page');

            // Find all expandable boxes
            const expandableBoxes = document.querySelectorAll('.expandable');
            console.log('Found expandable boxes:', expandableBoxes.length);

            if (expandableBoxes.length === 0) {
                console.warn('No expandable boxes found. Check if the .expandable class is applied correctly.');
                return;
            }

            // Add click event listeners to each expandable box
            expandableBoxes.forEach(box => {
                box.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    console.log('Box clicked:', box.querySelector('h2').textContent);
                    const isExpanded = box.classList.contains('expanded');

                    // Collapse all other boxes
                    expandableBoxes.forEach(otherBox => {
                        otherBox.classList.remove('expanded');
                    });

                    // Toggle the clicked box
                    if (!isExpanded) {
                        box.classList.add('expanded');
                    }
                });

                // Prevent hover effects when expanded
                box.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
                    if (box.classList.contains('expanded')) {
                        console.log('Box is expanded, disabling hover effects for:', box.querySelector('h2').textContent);
                        const scrollingText = box.querySelector('.scrolling-text');
                        const staticText = box.querySelector('.static-text');
                        if (scrollingText) scrollingText.style.display = 'none';
                        if (staticText) staticText.style.display = 'none';
                    }
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">
            Back
            <img src="/stuff/icon/undo_teal.svg" alt="Back Icon">
        </a>

        <div class="about-header">
            <% if (about) { %>
                <h1><%= about.title %></h1>
                <p>Learn more about our journey and what drives us.</p>
            <% } else { %>
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <p>Learn more about our journey and what drives us.</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content expandable">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <% if (about) { %>
                <p class="static-text"><%= about.descriptionTeaser %></p>
                <div class="scrolling-text">
                    <span><%= about.description %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="expanded-content">
                    <%= about.description %>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <p class="static-text">Passionate about travel, we curate personalized journeys worldwide.</p>
                <div class="scrolling-text">
                    <span>We are a passionate team dedicated to creating unforgettable travel experiences. With years of expertise, we curate journeys that inspire and delight.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="expanded-content">
                    We are a passionate team dedicated to creating unforgettable travel experiences. With years of expertise, we curate journeys that inspire and delight.
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content expandable">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <% if (about) { %>
                <p class="static-text"><%= about.missionTeaser %></p>
                <div class="scrolling-text">
                    <span><%= about.mission %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="expanded-content">
                    <%= about.mission %>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <p class="static-text">Inspiring wanderlust with seamless, sustainable travel experiences.</p>
                <div class="scrolling-text">
                    <span>To inspire and empower travelers to explore the world with confidence, creating memories that last a lifetime.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="expanded-content">
                    To inspire and empower travelers to explore the world with confidence, creating memories that last a lifetime.
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content non-expandable">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3>Passion</h3>
                    <p>We love what we do and are driven by a passion for travel and exploration.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3>Integrity</h3>
                    <p>We believe in transparency and honesty in all our dealings.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3>Excellence</h3>
                    <p>We strive for the highest standards in every journey we curate.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>